  "ai_usage": "Use for atmospheric, premium SaaS/AI landings. The aurora is three blurred radial gradients on a fixed layer, each drifting on its own keyframe; glass surfaces use backdrop-filter blur over it. Recolor via --a1/--a2/--a3. Keep text on solid-ish glass for contrast. Replace the hero mock and feature copy. Reduced-motion safe.",
  "path": "effects/website-templates/aurora-saas.html",
  "source": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\" />\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\" />\n<title>Aurora UI — SaaS</title>\n<script type=\"application/json\" id=\"effect-meta\">\n{\n  \"id\": \"aurora-saas\",\n  \"title\": \"Aurora UI — SaaS\",\n  \"summary\": \"A dreamy SaaS landing in the Aurora UI trend: an animated gradient-mesh backdrop, frosted-glass nav and cards, and an oversized gradient headline.\",\n  \"description\": \"Aurora UI (named for the northern lights) is one of 2026's signature looks — soft, animated gradient meshes glowing behind glassmorphic surfaces. This is a full SaaS landing built on it: drifting multi-radial mesh, a glass sticky nav, a giant gradient hero headline, glass feature cards, and a metrics band.\",\n  \"theme\": \"website-templates\",\n  \"categories\": [\"template\", \"landing\", \"saas\"],\n  \"tags\": [\"aurora-ui\", \"gradient-mesh\", \"glassmorphism\", \"saas\", \"dark\", \"2026-trend\", \"full-page\"],\n  \"tech\": [\"html\", \"css\", \"js\"],\n  \"era\": \"2020s\",\n  \"difficulty\": \"intermediate\",\n  \"dependencies\": [],\n  \"browser_support\": \"All modern browsers (backdrop-filter, CSS animations).\",\n  \"performance_notes\": \"Three animated radial-gradient layers + IntersectionObserver reveals. No images or libraries. Mesh animation pauses under reduced-motion.\",\n  \"accessibility_notes\": \"Semantic landmarks, focus-visible rings, contrast preserved over the dark mesh, prefers-reduced-motion disables the drift and reveals.\",\n  \"customization\": [\n    { \"name\": \"--a1/--a2/--a3\", \"description\": \"The three aurora colors\", \"default\": \"violet / teal / pink\" },\n    { \"name\": \"mesh keyframes\", \"description\": \"Drift speed/positions\", \"default\": \"26s loops\" }\n  ],\n  \"variations\": [\"Light aurora (raise lightness, lower opacity)\", \"Two-color mesh\", \"Static mesh (drop the animation)\"],\n  \"related\": [\"animated-gradient\",\"glass-navbar\",\"gradient-text\"],\n  \"ai_usage\": \"Use for atmospheric, premium SaaS/AI landings. The aurora is three blurred radial gradients on a fixed layer, each drifting on its own keyframe; glass surfaces use backdrop-filter blur over it. Recolor via --a1/--a2/--a3. Keep text on solid-ish glass for contrast. Replace the hero mock and feature copy. Reduced-motion safe.\"\n}\n</script>\n<style>\n  :root{--bg:#06060d;--text:#eef0fb;--muted:#9aa0c0;--line:rgba(255,255,255,.1);\n    --a1:#7c5cff;--a2:#2dd4bf;--a3:#ff6ec7;--glass:rgba(255,255,255,.055);--radius:20px;}\n  *{box-sizing:border-box}html{scroll-behavior:smooth}\n  body{margin:0;background:var(--bg);color:var(--text);font-family:\"Inter\",system-ui,-apple-system,sans-serif;line-height:1.6;overflow-x:hidden}\n  a{color:inherit;text-decoration:none}\n  /* aurora mesh */\n  .aurora{position:fixed;inset:-20%;z-index:-1;filter:blur(70px);opacity:.85}\n  .aurora i{position:absolute;width:48vw;height:48vw;border-radius:50%;mix-blend-mode:screen;will-change:transform}\n  .aurora i:nth-child(1){background:var(--a1);left:-5%;top:-5%;animation:d1 26s ease-in-out infinite}\n  .aurora i:nth-child(2){background:var(--a2);right:-8%;top:10%;animation:d2 30s ease-in-out infinite}\n  .aurora i:nth-child(3){background:var(--a3);left:25%;bottom:-15%;animation:d3 34s ease-in-out infinite}\n  @keyframes d1{50%{transform:translate(20vw,18vh) scale(1.25)}}\n  @keyframes d2{50%{transform:translate(-16vw,12vh) scale(1.15)}}\n  @keyframes d3{50%{transform:translate(10vw,-18vh) scale(1.3)}}\n  .wrap{max-width:1120px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 1.4rem}\n  nav{position:sticky;top:0;z-index:10;backdrop-filter:blur(16px) saturate(1.4);background:rgba(8,8,16,.45);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line)}\n  nav .wrap{display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;height:68px}\n  .brand{font-weight:800;font-size:1.15rem;letter-spacing:-.01em}\n  .brand b{background:linear-gradient(100deg,var(--a1),var(--a2),var(--a3));-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;color:transparent}\n  .links{display:flex;gap:1.6rem;align-items:center}.links a{color:var(--muted);font-size:.93rem;font-weight:500}.links a:hover{color:var(--text)}\n  .btn{display:inline-block;font-weight:600;border-radius:999px;padding:.6rem 1.2rem;background:linear-gradient(100deg,var(--a1),var(--a3));color:#fff;border:none;cursor:pointer;transition:transform .15s,box-shadow .15s}\n  .btn:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);box-shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(124,92,255,.4)}\n  .btn.glass{background:var(--glass);border:1px solid var(--line);backdrop-filter:blur(8px)}\n  .btn:focus-visible{outline:2px solid var(--a2);outline-offset:3px}\n  .hero{text-align:center;padding:7rem 0 5rem}\n  .pill{display:inline-flex;gap:.5rem;align-items:center;font-size:.8rem;color:var(--muted);background:var(--glass);border:1px solid var(--line);backdrop-filter:blur(8px);padding:.4rem .9rem;border-radius:999px}\n  .pill .dot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--a2);box-shadow:0 0 10px var(--a2)}\n  h1{font-size:clamp(2.6rem,7vw,5.2rem);line-height:1.02;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.03em;margin:1.2rem 0 .8rem}\n  h1 .g{background:linear-gradient(100deg,var(--a1),var(--a2),var(--a3));-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;color:transparent}\n  .sub{color:var(--muted);font-size:1.2rem;max-width:50ch;margin:0 auto 2rem}\n  .ctas{display:flex;gap:.8rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}\n  .mock{max-width:920px;margin:3.5rem auto 0;aspect-ratio:16/9;border-radius:var(--radius);background:var(--glass);border:1px solid var(--line);backdrop-filter:blur(12px);box-shadow:0 40px 120px rgba(0,0,0,.6)}\n  section{padding:5rem 0}\n  .eyebrow{text-align:center;color:var(--a2);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.18em;text-transform:uppercase;font-size:.76rem}\n  h2{text-align:center;font-size:clamp(1.9rem,4vw,2.8rem);font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-.02em;margin:.6rem 0 2.6rem}\n  .cards{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:1.2rem}\n  .card{background:var(--glass);border:1px solid var(--line);backdrop-filter:blur(14px);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:1.6rem}\n  .card .ic{font-size:1.6rem}.card h3{margin:.6rem 0 .3rem;font-size:1.15rem}.card p{color:var(--muted);margin:0;font-size:.95rem}\n  .metrics{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:1rem;text-align:center;background:var(--glass);border:1px solid var(--line);backdrop-filter:blur(14px);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:2.2rem 1rem}\n  .metrics .n{font-size:clamp(2rem,4vw,3rem);font-weight:800;background:linear-gradient(100deg,var(--a1),var(--a2));-webkit-background-clip:text;background-clip:text;color:transparent}\n  .metrics .l{color:var(--muted);font-size:.9rem}\n  footer{border-top:1px solid var(--line);color:var(--muted);text-align:center;padding:2.5rem 0;font-size:.9rem}\n  .reveal{opacity:0;transform:translateY(26px);transition:opacity .8s,transform .8s cubic-bezier(.2,.8,.2,1)}.reveal.in{opacity:1;transform:none}\n  @media(max-width:780px){.cards,.metrics{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}.links a:not(.btn){display:none}}\n  @media(prefers-reduced-motion:reduce){.aurora i{animation:none}.reveal{opacity:1;transform:none;transition:none}html{scroll-behavior:auto}}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n  <div class=\"aurora\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><i></i><i></i><i></i></div>\n  <nav><div class=\"wrap\">\n    <div class=\"brand\">✦ <b>Lumina</b></div>\n    <div class=\"links\"><a href=\"#\">Product</a><a href=\"#\">Solutions</a><a href=\"#\">Pricing</a><a href=\"#\">Docs</a><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\">Start free</a></div>\n  </div></nav>\n\n  <header class=\"hero\"><div class=\"wrap\">\n    <span class=\"pill\"><span class=\"dot\"></span> Now with realtime AI agents</span>\n    <h1>The workspace that <span class=\"g\">thinks ahead</span>.</h1>\n    <p class=\"sub\">Lumina unifies your docs, data, and workflows under one calm, intelligent surface — so your team moves at the speed of thought.</p>\n    <div class=\"ctas\"><a class=\"btn\" href=\"#\">Start free trial</a><a class=\"btn glass\" href=\"#\">Watch the film ↗</a></div>\n    <div class=\"mock\" role=\"img\" aria-label=\"Product screenshot placeholder\"></div>\n  </div></header>\n\n  <section><div class=\"wrap\">\n    <p class=\"eyebrow reveal\">Why teams switch</p>\n    <h2 class=\"reveal\">Built for flow, not friction</h2>\n    <div class=\"cards\">\n      <div class=\"card reveal\"><div class=\"ic\">🌌</div><h3>Ambient intelligence</h3><p>Context-aware suggestions that surface the moment you need them — never before.</p></div>\n      <div class=\"card reveal\"><div class=\"ic\">⚡</div><h3>Instant everywhere</h3><p>Edge-synced and offline-first. Your work is there before you ask.</p></div>\n      <div class=\"card reveal\"><div class=\"ic\">🔒</div><h3>Private by design</h3><p>End-to-end encryption and zero data training, by default.</p></div>\n    </div>\n  </div></section>\n\n  <section><div class=\"wrap\">\n    <div class=\"metrics reveal\">\n      <div><div class=\"n\">2.4M</div><div class=\"l\">active users</div></div>\n      <div><div class=\"n\">99.99%</div><div class=\"l\">uptime</div></div>\n      <div><div class=\"n\">11ms</div><div class=\"l\">p95 latency</div></div>\n      <div><div class=\"n\">4.9★</div><div class=\"l\">avg rating</div></div>\n    </div>\n  </div></section>\n\n  <footer><div class=\"wrap\">© <span id=\"yr\"></span> Lumina, Inc. · Made under the northern lights.</div></footer>\n  <script>\n    document.getElementById('yr').textContent=new Date().getFullYear();\n    var io=new IntersectionObserver(function(es){es.forEach(function(e){if(e.isIntersecting){e.target.classList.add('in');io.unobserve(e.target)}})},{threshold:.15});\n    document.querySelectorAll('.reveal').forEach(function(el){io.observe(el)});\n  </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n"
}
